{"tid":2056534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男病患腹痛求診　X光一照肚子裡「有條完整吳郭魚」：不小心坐在魚上","createTime":"2020-06-08T18:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T01:03:45.000Z","uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8aa535126c6332ede523f6c1ff5a5b8b22c29b4","tid":2056534,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:21:23.000Z","msg":"「城會玩」，相信這個網絡熱詞大家都不陌生，這個詞的本意是諷刺某些人做的事情常人無法理解。但是一般這個詞更多是朋友間的相互調侃，但是這個世界就是那麼的神奇，林子大了，什麼樣的人都有，他們做出一些常人不能理解的事情也就見怪不怪了，但是今天小編要說的這件事情就特別「難以理解」了，因為近日一男子腹中竟出現一條完整的吳郭魚，這到底是什麼情況呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.edge435.com/uploads/20200608/73/7362AFB4D105w498h280.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.edge435.com%2Fuploads%2F20200608%2F73%2F7362AFB4D105w498h280.jpeg&h=ec1b710a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月2日上午，一男子因為腹痛去醫院就診，但是在醫生問具體什麼位置疼痛是男子卻支支吾吾說不出個所以然，但也許是疼痛太厲害了，男子低聲說到，因為自己不小心坐到了一條吳郭魚身上，導致其進入了自己的直腸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.edge435.com/uploads/20200608/1F/1F1A55F16058w499h278.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.edge435.com%2Fuploads%2F20200608%2F1F%2F1F1A55F16058w499h278.jpeg&h=a69add4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為事情緊急，醫生馬上安排其拍片查看具體情況，從拍出來的片子可以明顯看到有一條完整的魚在男子體內，並且魚頭最寬處已達30.5mm了，隨後醫生立馬安排手術將魚從男子體內取出。<br />\n醫生在具體瞭解後得知，在魚進去之後，男子打算自己取出來的，但是因為吳郭魚背鰭非常堅硬，進去容易出來難，隨著時間一分一秒的過去，男子出現腹痛並且逐漸加重，無可奈何的情況下只得來到醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.edge435.com/uploads/20200608/52/52E2A8BB2FAEw498h283.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.edge435.com%2Fuploads%2F20200608%2F52%2F52E2A8BB2FAEw498h283.jpeg&h=849522fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是因為時間拖得太久，吳郭魚取出來時已經腐爛而且臭氣熏天，在場的醫護人員都忍不住嘔吐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.edge435.com/uploads/20200608/4D/4D331C4DFA54w439h787.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.edge435.com%2Fuploads%2F20200608%2F4D%2F4D331C4DFA54w439h787.jpeg&h=7d4cb03c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際上吳郭魚就是我們最常見的魚，大家可能沒有這個概念，我找了一張圖，我們全體編輯對著這條魚呆了半天，實在想不到人類的&hellip;&hellip;是怎麼塞得進去的？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.edge435.com/uploads/20200608/29/29B8CF659AF3w640h360.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.edge435.com%2Fuploads%2F20200608%2F29%2F29B8CF659AF3w640h360.jpeg&h=fcab1d57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51e54b1a2dc4e263d8479e28111cd87a09272112","tid":2056534,"uid":227271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"點解我會諗左韓國瑜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FA8h63U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFA8h63U.jpg&h=1b7b84fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eea0a80c5e7dc5b0fe703df70911884d30e4245","tid":2056534,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"可以影到post上內聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d88d5adf3767bdf196396f369021b8f04b4cba9","tid":2056534,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2eea0a80c5e7dc5b0fe703df70911884d30e4245","tid":2056534,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"可以影到post上內聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"支那嘛，乜柒都影得啦，邊有保障"},{"pid":"b927d82ff484e60a168eecbb8fdb1f3a5e70b06f","tid":2056534,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95444d494e8f925eb7edca8a239e6a121cdd31c5","tid":2056534,"uid":10063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"RIP 魚,下世小心D"},{"pid":"d1bb6007310fda70a3e8b979a3dd7fb9e2c86c6b","tid":2056534,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c